OL,3,CNumber of confirmed Cryptosporidium
OL,4,Ccases linked to Farm Shop reaches 47
OL,6,FThe number of cases of Cryptosporidium
OL,7,Finfection linked to a Farm shop in the
OL,8,FVale of Glamorgan has reached 47.
OL,10,FOn Wednesday it was reported that
OL,11,Fhealth authorities were investigating
OL,12,F28 cases of Cryptosporidium infection
OL,13,Fin people who attended calf and lamb
OL,14,Ffeeding and petting sessions at
OL,15,FCowbridge Farm Shop, Marlborough
OL,16,FGrange Farm, Cross Ways, Cowbridge
OL,17,FCF71 7LJ.
