OL,6,FPublic Health wales are warning that
OL,7,Fdue to the incubation period of the
OL,8,Finfection, they expect that this
OL,9,Fnumber may increase in the coming
OL,10,Fweeks.
OL,12,FThey say the Outbreak Control Team
OL,13,Fcontinues to work closely with the
OL,14,Fpremises to investigate this outbreak.
OL,16,FThe farm has voluntarily ceased all
OL,17,Fpublic animal feeding activities and
OL,18,Fis cooperating with the investigation.
