OL,6,FCryptosporidium is a parasite that can
OL,7,Fcause gastrointestinal illness, often
OL,8,Fassociated with contact with animals,
OL,9,Fespecially young farm animals such as
OL,10,Fcalves and lambs.
OL,12,FSu Mably, Consultant in Health
OL,13,Fprotection for Public Health Wales
OL,14,Fsaid "we are continuing to investigate
OL,15,Fthis outbreak with our partners.
OL,17,F"While the infection is usually mild
OL,18,Fand self-limiting, it can be more
OL,19,Fserious in young children or people
OL,20,Fwith weakened immune systems.
